{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"枠のシャドウや角丸が抜けている","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/orphaned/Web/Compatibility_FAQ/No_Decoreation_Shown.html","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概要","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p>枠のシャドウ(影付け装飾)や角丸(アイコンやボタンの角の丸み)が表示されません。</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/9987/0204.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"要因","title":"要因","isH3":false,"content":"<p>要因の代表例として以下があります。</p>\n<ol>\n  <li>\n    <strong>ベンダープレフィックス</strong>\n    webkit ブラウザ向けの記述がされている場合、この現象が発生します。\n    例えば、以下のような場合です。\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>シャドウの場合</strong>\n        <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.hoge</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 1px 2px <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.4<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n      </li>\n      <li><strong>角丸の場合</strong>\n        <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.hoge</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-moz-border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 6px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 6px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ol>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"解決策","title":"解決策","isH3":false,"content":"<p>要因の解決策の代表例として以下があります。</p>\n<ol>\n  <li>\n    <strong>ベンダープレフィックス</strong>\n    他ブラウザで互換性を維持する為に、以下のような<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/box-shadow\">box-shadow</a>プロパティ、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/border-radius\">border-radius</a>プロパティの記述を追加します。\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>シャドウの場合</strong>\n        <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.hoge</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 1px 2px <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.4<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 1px 2px <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.4<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n      </li>\n      <li><strong>角丸の場合</strong>\n        <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.hoge</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-moz-border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 6px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 6px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 6px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ol>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"メリット","title":"メリット","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>他のブラウザでも互換性を維持することができます。\n    <ul>\n      <li>追記のみの対応のため改修が容易です。</li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/orphaned/Web/Compatibility_FAQ\">戻る</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"概要"},{"text":"要因","id":"要因"},{"text":"解決策","id":"解決策"},{"text":"メリット","id":"メリット"}],"summary":"枠のシャドウ(影付け装飾)や角丸(アイコンやボタンの角の丸み)が表示されません。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","source":{"folder":"ja/orphaned/web/compatibility_faq/no_decoreation_shown.html","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/orphaned/web/compatibility_faq/no_decoreation_shown.html/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/orphaned/Web/Compatibility_FAQ","title":"サイト表示互換性に関するノウハウ"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/orphaned/Web/Compatibility_FAQ/No_Decoreation_Shown.html","title":"枠のシャドウや角丸が抜けている"}],"pageTitle":"枠のシャドウや角丸が抜けている | MDN","noIndexing":true}}